{"article_id":"jgnAt4arNYP39tZa","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"Calling it \" the worst day of his political life , \"","depth":5},{"id":1,"text":"Minnesota Democratic Sen. Al Franken said Thursday","depth":7},{"id":2,"text":"he will resign from the U.S. Senate","depth":7},{"id":3,"text":"following a wave of sexual misconduct allegations against him","depth":7},{"id":4,"text":"that ranged from groping to forcibly trying to kiss women .","depth":7},{"id":5,"text":"Franken ,","depth":7},{"id":6,"text":"who said","depth":8},{"id":7,"text":"that some of the complaints against him were \" simply not true \"","depth":9},{"id":8,"text":"and that he remembers others \" differently , \"","depth":9},{"id":9,"text":"also took a parting shot at President Trump .","depth":6},{"id":10,"text":"\" There is some irony in the fact","depth":8},{"id":11,"text":"that I am leaving office","depth":8},{"id":12,"text":"while a man","depth":10},{"id":13,"text":"who has bragged on tape about his history of sexual assault","depth":10},{"id":14,"text":"sits in the Oval Office ,","depth":9},{"id":15,"text":"and a man","depth":10},{"id":16,"text":"who has repeatedly preyed on young girls","depth":10},{"id":17,"text":"campaigns for the Senate with the full supoort of his party , \"","depth":9},{"id":18,"text":"Franken said ,","depth":7},{"id":19,"text":"referring to Trump and Roy Moore , the Republican candidate for Senate in Alabama .","depth":7},{"id":20,"text":"About 18 Democratic senators , staff and family members were on hand for the announcement .","depth":7},{"id":21,"text":"Some sat stone-faced","depth":8},{"id":22,"text":"while others cried during the 11-minute speech .","depth":8},{"id":23,"text":"His staff were lined up in the back of the chamber .","depth":6},{"id":24,"text":"Alaska Sen. Dan Sullivan was the only Republican senator present .","depth":7},{"id":25,"text":"New York Sen. Kirsten Gillibrand and Minnesota Sen. Amy Klobuchar were also in attendance .","depth":9},{"id":26,"text":"They were among the lengthy list of Democrats","depth":10},{"id":27,"text":"pressuring Franken to resign .","depth":10},{"id":28,"text":"\" As he and I discussed yesterday ,","depth":10},{"id":29,"text":"this is the right decision , \"","depth":10},{"id":30,"text":"Klobuchar said in a statement .","depth":9},{"id":31,"text":"Virginia Democratic Sen. Tim Kaine said","depth":8},{"id":32,"text":"he had a `` detailed conversation '' with Franken Wednesday evening .","depth":8},{"id":33,"text":"`` He did what I suggested","depth":11},{"id":34,"text":"--","depth":11},{"id":35,"text":"and he did the right thing --","depth":10},{"id":36,"text":"so I 'm just going to leave it there , ''","depth":9},{"id":37,"text":"Kaine said .","depth":8},{"id":38,"text":"It will be up to Minnesota Democratic Gov . Mark Dayton to appoint a successor .","depth":6},{"id":39,"text":"Multiple sources reported","depth":7},{"id":40,"text":"that the likely candidate could be Democratic Lt. Gov . Tina Smith , a close ally of Franken .","depth":7},{"id":41,"text":"The successor would serve","depth":6},{"id":42,"text":"until a special election is held in 2018","depth":7},{"id":43,"text":"to determine","depth":8},{"id":44,"text":"who would fill the final two years of Franken ' s term .","depth":8},{"id":45,"text":"On Wednesday , Franken faced a tidal wave of resignation calls by members of his own party .","depth":5},{"id":46,"text":"By mid-afternoon , 23 of them wanted him gone .","depth":6},{"id":47,"text":"By Thursday , the number had grown to 36 .","depth":6},{"id":48,"text":"Her sentiment was echoed by Sens . Kamala Harris of California , Marie Hirono of Hawaii , Claire McCaskill of Missouri , Tammy Baldwin of Wisconsin , Maria Cantwell of Washington , Debbie Stabenow of Michigan , Maggie Hassan of New Hampshire , Tammy Duckworth of Illinois and Heidi Heitkamp of North Dakota .","depth":5},{"id":49,"text":"\" Sexual harassment and misconduct should not be allowed by anyone","depth":9},{"id":50,"text":"and should not occur anywhere .","depth":9},{"id":51,"text":"I believe","depth":10},{"id":52,"text":"the best thing for Senator Franken to do","depth":11},{"id":53,"text":"is step down , \"","depth":11},{"id":54,"text":"Harris , D-Calif. , said .","depth":9},{"id":55,"text":"Hassan , D-N.H. , tweeted ,","depth":8},{"id":56,"text":"\" It is clear that Al Franken has engaged in a pattern of egregious and unacceptable behavior toward women .","depth":9},{"id":57,"text":"He should resign . ''","depth":9},{"id":58,"text":"\" It now appears Senator Franken has lost the support of his colleagues , and most importantly , his constituents , \"","depth":8},{"id":59,"text":"McConnell said .","depth":8},{"id":60,"text":"\" I do not believe","depth":9},{"id":61,"text":"he can effectively serve the people of Minnesota in the U.S. Senate any longer , \"","depth":9},{"id":62,"text":"he added .","depth":8},{"id":63,"text":"The Minneapolis Star Tribune , the largest newspaper in Franken ' s home state , called for his immediate resignation late Wednesday .","depth":6},{"id":64,"text":"They questioned his ability","depth":8},{"id":65,"text":"to \" function effectively \"","depth":8},{"id":66,"text":"after \" losing the confidence of so many colleagues .","depth":7},{"id":67,"text":"\" If this is to be an actual turning point in our culture ,","depth":7},{"id":68,"text":"there must be real and lasting consequences to behaviors","depth":8},{"id":69,"text":"that never should have been accepted , \"","depth":8},{"id":70,"text":"the editorial board wrote .","depth":6},{"id":71,"text":"\" That these incidents came so late in Franken ' s life should make him all the more accountable .","depth":5},{"id":72,"text":"Instead , he has mostly offered hollow apologies","depth":6},{"id":73,"text":"that failed to acknowledge what happened . \"","depth":6},{"id":74,"text":"Franken ' s political career has been in peril","depth":3},{"id":75,"text":"since California radio broadcaster Leeann Tweeden posted a blog","depth":7},{"id":76,"text":"detailing","depth":8},{"id":77,"text":"how he kissed and groped her","depth":9},{"id":78,"text":"without her consent in 2006 .","depth":9},{"id":79,"text":"She also tweeted a picture","depth":7},{"id":80,"text":"showing a grinning Franken","depth":8},{"id":81,"text":"standing over her","depth":10},{"id":82,"text":"as she sleeps ,","depth":10},{"id":83,"text":"his hands over her breasts .","depth":9},{"id":84,"text":"Franken has since apologized ,","depth":7},{"id":85,"text":"but other allegations from seven additional women have surfaced since Tweeden ' s claims .","depth":7},{"id":86,"text":"The latest was a woman","depth":7},{"id":87,"text":"who claimed","depth":8},{"id":88,"text":"she was groped at a Media Matters party during the first Obama inauguration .","depth":8},{"id":89,"text":"Before that , another woman accused Franken of forcibly trying to kiss her","depth":6},{"id":90,"text":"- this time after a taping of his radio show in 2006 .","depth":6},{"id":91,"text":"The woman ,","depth":10},{"id":92,"text":"who spoke to Politico ,","depth":10},{"id":93,"text":"claims","depth":9},{"id":94,"text":"Franken pursued her","depth":9},{"id":95,"text":"after her boss had left","depth":10},{"id":96,"text":"and she was collecting her things .","depth":10},{"id":97,"text":"The woman was in her 20s at the time .","depth":7},{"id":98,"text":"The accuser ,","depth":10},{"id":99,"text":"who was not identified ,","depth":10},{"id":100,"text":"said","depth":9},{"id":101,"text":"Franken tried to kiss her","depth":9},{"id":102,"text":"but that she ducked .","depth":9},{"id":103,"text":"Franken , a former `` Saturday Night Live '' performer","depth":11},{"id":104,"text":"who was a host on the now-defunct `` Air America '' radio network at the time ,","depth":11},{"id":105,"text":"allegedly followed up","depth":10},{"id":106,"text":"by telling her","depth":10},{"id":107,"text":"it was his \" right as an entertainer . \"","depth":10},{"id":108,"text":"\" He was between me and the door","depth":11},{"id":109,"text":"and he was coming at me","depth":12},{"id":110,"text":"to kiss me , \"","depth":12},{"id":111,"text":"she told Politico .","depth":10},{"id":112,"text":"\" It was very quick","depth":10},{"id":113,"text":"and I think","depth":13},{"id":114,"text":"my brain had to work really hard","depth":13},{"id":115,"text":"to be like","depth":13},{"id":116,"text":"' Wait , what is happening ? '","depth":13},{"id":117,"text":"But I knew","depth":13},{"id":118,"text":"whatever was happening was not right","depth":13},{"id":119,"text":"and I ducked . \"","depth":12},{"id":120,"text":"The calls","depth":5},{"id":121,"text":"for Franken to step down","depth":5},{"id":122,"text":"came after Rep. John Conyers , D-Mich. , retired","depth":5},{"id":123,"text":"following numerous allegations of sexual misconduct against him .","depth":5},{"id":124,"text":"In Alabama , several women have accused Moore , the Senate Republican candidate , of sexual misconduct","depth":6},{"id":125,"text":"when they were in their teens ,","depth":6},{"id":126,"text":"including one","depth":6},{"id":127,"text":"who said","depth":7},{"id":128,"text":"she was 14","depth":8},{"id":129,"text":"when Moore molested her .","depth":8},{"id":130,"text":"Trump","depth":6},{"id":131,"text":"-- who had multiple allegations of sexual harassment against himself","depth":7},{"id":132,"text":"when running for president --","depth":7},{"id":133,"text":"has endorsed Moore .","depth":5}],"relations":[{"parent":267,"left":207,"right":266,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":207,"left":178,"right":206,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":178,"left":153,"right":177,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":153,"left":138,"right":152,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":138,"left":0,"right":137,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":137,"left":135,"right":136,"relation":"context","nu